the eight‐headed serpent (dating from Tenpō 5, January) * Ema commemorating Mt. Fuji ascents (dating from Keien 7, June) * Ema depicting the pilgrimage to Ise (by Fujigoro and Murata Masatarō, dating from Keien 3, March) == Access == * From the [[Seibu Ikebukuro Line]] at {{ill|Hayamachi Station|ja|保谷駅|qq=draft|qq=draft}} South Exit, take the {{ill|Midori Bus|ja|みどりバス|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to “Bessobashi” (a 3‑minute walk from the bus stop)＜ref＞{{Cite web|url=https://www.city.nerima.tokyo.jp/kankomoyoshi/annai/rekishiwoshiru/rekishibunkazai/kakarikara/prnerima/dai30.pdf|title=Nerima Cultural Property No.30|publisher=City of Nerima|accessdate=2019-11-02|format=PDF}}＜/ref＞ * Or, from the [[Toei Oedo Line]] at {{ill|Hikarigaoka Station|ja|光が丘駅|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, take a bus for 19 minutes. == References ==
{{Reflist}}
